  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Only Wish</h2><br>Welcome to \"Only Wish\", the next-generation advancement of the acclaimed \"Only Up\" genre. Embark on an unparalleled gaming journey enriched with breathtaking landscapes, groundbreaking gameplay, and an array of unique features that set it apart.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover Hidden Realms</h2>Delve into the heart of mystery. Every door you encounter conceals secrets and untold stories, beckoning you to discover what lies beyond.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/8bb8150bffe3074f57fea6ced63f4272.poster.avif?t=1757567042\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/8bb8150bffe3074f57fea6ced63f4272.webm?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/8bb8150bffe3074f57fea6ced63f4272.mp4?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Revolutionary Vehicular Exploration</h2>Why limit your exploration to walking? Jump into a diverse selection of vehicles and traverse the vast expanses of our world. Feel the pulse of authentic driving dynamics and harness the full power of vehicle propulsion.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/e994101089a1283cb7a4da17580eaaaf.poster.avif?t=1757567042\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/e994101089a1283cb7a4da17580eaaaf.webm?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/e994101089a1283cb7a4da17580eaaaf.mp4?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engaging NPC Dialogues</h2><br>Deepen your immersion with intricate interactions from our varied NPCs. Each conversation is designed to amplify your engagement and propel the storyline. Engage with characters, unravel hidden tales, and make pivotal decisions that could alter the trajectory of your adventure. Enter a realm where dialogue is an art, and every character weaves their own unique narrative.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/ca6f8ebdba302d57fbae153cc483c719.poster.avif?t=1757567042\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/ca6f8ebdba302d57fbae153cc483c719.webm?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/ca6f8ebdba302d57fbae153cc483c719.mp4?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Only Wish</h2><br>Welcome to \"Only Wish\", the next-generation advancement of the acclaimed \"Only Up\" genre. Embark on an unparalleled gaming journey enriched with breathtaking landscapes, groundbreaking gameplay, and an array of unique features that set it apart.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover Hidden Realms</h2>Delve into the heart of mystery. Every door you encounter conceals secrets and untold stories, beckoning you to discover what lies beyond.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/8bb8150bffe3074f57fea6ced63f4272.poster.avif?t=1757567042\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/8bb8150bffe3074f57fea6ced63f4272.webm?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/8bb8150bffe3074f57fea6ced63f4272.mp4?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Revolutionary Vehicular Exploration</h2>Why limit your exploration to walking? Jump into a diverse selection of vehicles and traverse the vast expanses of our world. Feel the pulse of authentic driving dynamics and harness the full power of vehicle propulsion.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/e994101089a1283cb7a4da17580eaaaf.poster.avif?t=1757567042\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/e994101089a1283cb7a4da17580eaaaf.webm?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/e994101089a1283cb7a4da17580eaaaf.mp4?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engaging NPC Dialogues</h2><br>Deepen your immersion with intricate interactions from our varied NPCs. Each conversation is designed to amplify your engagement and propel the storyline. Engage with characters, unravel hidden tales, and make pivotal decisions that could alter the trajectory of your adventure. Enter a realm where dialogue is an art, and every character weaves their own unique narrative.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/ca6f8ebdba302d57fbae153cc483c719.poster.avif?t=1757567042\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/ca6f8ebdba302d57fbae153cc483c719.webm?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2542010/extras/ca6f8ebdba302d57fbae153cc483c719.mp4?t=1757567042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
